			<div class="fl-col fl-node-xq8dmiv602tf fl-col-bg-color" data-node="xq8dmiv602tf">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-heading fl-node-p60bc9kts4il" data-node="p60bc9kts4il">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<h2 class="fl-heading default">
		<span class="fl-heading-text">Local builder with national expertise</span>
	</h2>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-uiea92stfl8r" data-node="uiea92stfl8r">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p><span data-teams="true">Messer provides unmatched leadership of complex commercial construction projects. For more than 90 years, our transformational investment in people, communities and Innovative building solutions has enhanced the landscape of the places we call home. As a result, we’ve become the trusted builder for hundreds of organizations across the Midwest and Southeast</span>.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#"><strong>Employee Ownership:</strong></a> <span data-teams="true">As an employee-owned company since 1990, we're dedicated to building for long-term success</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></li>
<li><a href="#"><strong>Community Investment:</strong></a> <span data-teams="true">Investing in the people and organizations where we live and work is ingrained in Messer's culture.</span></li>
<li><a href="#"><strong>Leadership:</strong></a> <span data-teams="true">Our Executives, Officers, Senior Managers and Board of Directors lead the way.</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-row fl-row-fixed-width fl-row-bg-none fl-node-kowcn1ajd7m6 fl-row-default-height fl-row-align-center" data-node="kowcn1ajd7m6">
	<div class="fl-row-content-wrap">
						<div class="fl-row-content fl-row-full-width fl-node-content">
		
<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-zi70efnxjw3s" data-node="zi70efnxjw3s">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-uxabit45v0gn fl-col-bg-color" data-node="uxabit45v0gn">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-accordion fl-node-klto4fzxwjvh" data-node="klto4fzxwjvh">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		
<div class="fl-accordion fl-accordion-small fl-accordion-collapse">
