					<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Zero Injury: </b>Personal commitment to provide a safe work environment every day</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Ownership: </b>Accountable for our actions and results</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Leadership: </b>Influence people to achieve positive results</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Integrity: </b>Ethical and transparent in everything we do</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Diversity and Inclusion: </b>Seek and embrace people with different backgrounds and perspectives</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Customer Focus: </b>Understand our customers and exceed expectations</p>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1">
<p class="p2"><b>Craftforce: </b>Building with professionalism and pride</p>
</li>
</ul>
