<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-78lmez0nrcsk" data-node="78lmez0nrcsk">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-pyajk93c7wez fl-col-bg-color" data-node="pyajk93c7wez">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-heading fl-node-fr1gnmsk69q2" data-node="fr1gnmsk69q2">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<h2 class="fl-heading subheading text-green">
		<span class="fl-heading-text">HISTORY</span>
	</h2>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
	</div>

<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-9cqv78ymrwbt" data-node="9cqv78ymrwbt">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-qc43j6kb1pox fl-col-bg-color" data-node="qc43j6kb1pox">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-heading fl-node-qmygo8rxus4h" data-node="qmygo8rxus4h">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<h2 class="fl-heading default">
		<span class="fl-heading-text">A solid foundation for today and tomorrow</span>
	</h2>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-x23huc956rw7" data-node="x23huc956rw7">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p>Messer was founded in 1932 and became employee-owned in 1990.<br>
Here are several milestones and achievements from the early days of the company all the way to the present.</p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-row fl-row-full-width fl-row-bg-color fl-node-1sh4tvp7e2o8 fl-row-default-height fl-row-align-center" data-node="1sh4tvp7e2o8">
	<div class="fl-row-content-wrap">
						<div class="fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content">
		
<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-3uqd2g6t8vew" data-node="3uqd2g6t8vew">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-7fpqxg6muwdc fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="7fpqxg6muwdc">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-tyzhioswdxk3" data-node="tyzhioswdxk3">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span class="s1" style="font-size: 36px;"><b><span style="color: #305121;">1930s</span><span style="font-size: 32px;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-eo8wn25jrqxz" data-node="eo8wn25jrqxz">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-5614 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/f1b4969d4d0063.jpg" alt="Nashville Post Office" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="history-1930_basic-curved-sbs_nashville-post-office" srcset="/assets-f/img/f1b4969d4d0063.jpg 492w, /assets-f/img/b3a6fbd2b52b1b.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-2slrbz9ht4wq" data-node="2slrbz9ht4wq">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1">Frank Messer &amp; Sons, Inc. is founded by Frank Messer in 1932. The family-owned company focuses on public works, constructing the central post office in Nashville, Tennessee, the public library in Toledo, Ohio, and a number of schools in Cincinnati, Ohio.</p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-jxdi8eg0z6mu fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="jxdi8eg0z6mu">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-l9unw8yg47j3" data-node="l9unw8yg47j3">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span class="s1" style="font-size: 36px;"><b><span style="color: #305121;">1940s</span><span style="font-size: 32px;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-l6crfszt4eqb" data-node="l6crfszt4eqb">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-5615 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/66e9ad4f087c8b.jpg" alt="Wright Aeronautical Plant" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="history-1940_basic-curved-sbs_wright-aeronautical-plant" srcset="/assets-f/img/66e9ad4f087c8b.jpg 492w, /assets-f/img/fc0af263f96a0d.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-m756hqbt8y91" data-node="m756hqbt8y91">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1">Messer is awarded the contract to build the $37 million Wright Aeronautical Plant in Evendale, Ohio. It was considered at the time to be the largest building award ever let under one contract in the United States.</p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-d7c4rt2aj5yf fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="d7c4rt2aj5yf">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-zo1qfne785g6" data-node="zo1qfne785g6">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span style="font-size: 36px;"><b><span style="color: #305121;">1950-1970s</span><span style="font-size: 32px;">––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-5zj9ydbwoasv" data-node="5zj9ydbwoasv">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-5616 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/8f754ba3c8ce4a.jpg" alt="Armory" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="history-1950-70_basic-curved-sbs_armory" srcset="/assets-f/img/8f754ba3c8ce4a.jpg 492w, /assets-f/img/5c4f2f3bc6467d.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-rich-text fl-node-dpw9hctuflji" data-node="dpw9hctuflji">
	<p><span data-teams="true">Under the leadership of Frank’s son, Charles Messer, the company continues to grow&nbsp;with expertise shifting toward high-rise construction.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-v47uos20efr6 fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="v47uos20efr6">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-n8iem73yrg6q" data-node="n8iem73yrg6q">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span style="font-size: 36px;"><b><span style="color: #305121;">1980s</span><span style="font-size: 32px;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-u37azmpro0vi" data-node="u37azmpro0vi">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-5617 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/3b6e11864d35b2.jpg" alt="One Lytle Place" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="history-1980_basic-curved-sbs_lytle" srcset="/assets-f/img/3b6e11864d35b2.jpg 492w, /assets-f/img/c53cab19044f5f.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-rich-text fl-node-umx7e1dlkayi" data-node="umx7e1dlkayi">
	<p>Messer focuses on attracting and retaining high-performing construction professionals and building the company’s capacity for performance. The focus pays off, and in 1987, the company performs more than $100 million worth of construction for the first time in its history.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-row fl-row-full-width fl-row-bg-color fl-node-p9rvhk68lgu4 fl-row-default-height fl-row-align-center" data-node="p9rvhk68lgu4">
	<div class="fl-row-content-wrap">
						<div class="fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content">
		
<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-ry3zb8vkdj4w" data-node="ry3zb8vkdj4w">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-go7n1jv39rcd fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="go7n1jv39rcd">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-jcg6on8pr0e2" data-node="jcg6on8pr0e2">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span class="s1" style="font-size: 36px; color: #305121;"><b>1990s<span style="font-size: 32px; color: #000000;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-iujn4hsqr8kp" data-node="iujn4hsqr8kp">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-png">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-26669 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/1c50a1105142e6.png" alt="CCHMC Location A" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="CCHMC Location A" srcset="/assets-f/img/1c50a1105142e6.png 492w, /assets-f/img/7fdeed23174bc8.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-7k9ojidpwx1h" data-node="7k9ojidpwx1h">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1">Messer’s 99 employees purchase the company from the Messer family in 1990. The company begins to expand its footprint by opening regional offices in Lexington, Columbus and Dayton. <span data-teams="true">Each region’s employees live and work locally, preserving the company’s longtime commitment to delivering quality to customers. Rapid growth follows, and by 1997, Messer hits the $300 million in annual revenue for the first time.</span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-6fx4dsu2a9cp fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="6fx4dsu2a9cp">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-ndjbce6r45o7" data-node="ndjbce6r45o7">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span class="s1" style="font-size: 36px; color: #305121;"><b>2000s<span style="color: #000000; font-size: 32px;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-27ltxvgfuyeo" data-node="27ltxvgfuyeo">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-5619 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/7f8f63cd60eb2e.jpg" alt="Kentucky Transportation Cabinet Building" itemprop="image" height="468" width="492" title="history-2000_basic-curved-sbs_ky-transportation-cabint-building" srcset="/assets-f/img/7f8f63cd60eb2e.jpg 492w, /assets-f/img/ba10c17b88f873.webp 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-1i6p9zdgj2v7" data-node="1i6p9zdgj2v7">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p><span data-teams="true">The company changes its name to Messer Construction Co. with a growing regional footprint in Louisville, Knoxville, Indianapolis, and Nashville. Messer puts in place more than $500 million of revenue for the first time in its history and forms its Economic Inclusion department in 2005.</span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-a07z231ko5ly fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="a07z231ko5ly">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-7p9osa03th2q" data-node="7p9osa03th2q">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span style="font-size: 36px; color: #305121;"><b>2010s<span style="font-size: 32px; color: #000000;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-pde69tmk1bu5" data-node="pde69tmk1bu5">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-14892 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/423920c60c6781.jpg" alt="EGC" itemprop="image" height="1950" width="2050" title="history-2010_basic-curved-sbs_EGCv2" srcset="/assets-f/img/423920c60c6781.jpg 2050w, /assets-f/img/2b9bf2f3042f3e.webp 300w, /assets-f/img/39232a5688aced.webp 1024w, /assets-f/img/dba67a3af49df6.webp 768w, /assets-f/img/1a023e836387b8.webp 1536w, /assets-f/img/32c5b6194e9152.webp 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2050px) 100vw, 2050px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-rich-text fl-node-s8vp7wt2xk01" data-node="s8vp7wt2xk01">
	<p><span data-teams="true">Messer establishes its presence in North Carolina in Charlotte and Raleigh, as well as acquires EGC Construction. More than 25 years after becoming employee-owned, the company’s workforce has increased tenfold, its annual revenue has multiplied by more than eight, and it operates in 10 regions throughout the Midwest and Southeast.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-kr34zyxidtg2 fl-col-bg-color fl-col-small" data-node="kr34zyxidtg2">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-t3q5kfczyhgv" data-node="t3q5kfczyhgv">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p class="p1"><span style="font-size: 36px; color: #305121;"><b>2020s<span style="color: #000000; font-size: 32px;">–––––––––––</span></b></span></p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-bls81k4dfevo" data-node="bls81k4dfevo">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
	<div class="fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg">
				<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fl-photo-img wp-image-12796 size-full" src="/assets-f/img/354a867db0e324.jpg" alt="Messer Greenville" itemprop="image" height="975" width="1025" title="history-2020_basic-curved-sbs_greenville" srcset="/assets-f/img/354a867db0e324.jpg 1025w, /assets-f/img/c2ee2810f381b4.webp 300w, /assets-f/img/dd6d790377aa28.webp 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1025px) 100vw, 1025px">
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-rich-text fl-node-790heuoivf3b" data-node="790heuoivf3b">
	<p><span data-teams="true">2020 marks Messer's 30th year of employee-ownership and 90th year in business. In January 2023, Messer expands into South Carolina with a new regional office located in Greenville and serving the Upstate.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
    </div>
	
    </main>

